@startuml
title Session Management Flow Diagram

|Student|
start
:Request chat session list;

|System Handler|
:Query sessions for current user;
:Return session list,\ntitles, and chat scope summary;

|Student|
:Open one session for review;

|System Handler|
:Load session details and message history;
:Mark citations from deleted documents when needed;
:Return messages and scope label;

|Student|
:Review session history on UI;
if (Desired action?) then (Rename session)
  :Enter new session title;
  :Confirm rename request;
  |System Handler|
  :Verify session ownership;
  :Update session title in Database;
  |Student|
  :See updated title in session list;
else (Delete session)
  :Request session deletion;
  :Confirm delete warning;
  |System Handler|
  :Verify session ownership;
  :Delete session and related messages;
  :Return refreshed list;
  |Student|
  :See session list after deletion;
endif

stop
@enduml
